data.description: Welcome to 11 Cedar Gate Circle which is complete with a view of the lake!  Quietly tucked away in a circle with beautiful views of the lake.  Great open and bright floor plan with hardwood floors on the 1st and 2nd floors. Enjoy the updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, corian counters, backsplash.  Enjoy the evenings in the Family Room with a beautiful stone fireplace.  Kitchen / Breakfast area opens up to a spacious patio.  Nice sized sun drenched living room which flows into the dining room with built-in's which is perfect for a coffee bar!! Primary  bedroom features his /her closets with built-in organizers, private bathroom with his / her sinks and larger corner whirlpool tub/ shower! Secondary bedrooms are very spacious with large closets and bamboo wood floors. Updated hall bath is gorgeous! Finished basement with recreation room perfect for media room, exercise room, game room or play room. Large fenced in yard with patio great for entertaining. Great location to the common area lake access to enjoy fishing, smaller water craft or just enjoy the lake.  Enjoy the wonderful community of Prestbury with a pool, clubhouse, tennis courts and so much more!!
